rows.label: qev087402_MSG0001
rows.name: I heard he usually gets breakfast here, but I don'tâ€”[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0002
rows.name: Ah! Mustache man![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0003
rows.name: All right, let's get this over with.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0004
rows.name: He's done eating, but he's still sitting there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0005
rows.name: As Tatsu thought, sooo much free time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0006
rows.name: We're having trouble with ciniculas, sir.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0007
rows.name:
Ben, Miranda, and Cornell's team have been engaging them,
but with limited success.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0008
rows.name:
Ciniculas? They're a cinch.
Just snap that big horn off their melon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0009
rows.name:
That exposes an orange subdermal structure
that you can fry with a beam.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0010
rows.name: Just relax and have fun with it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0011
rows.name:
Sir, Sakuraba Industries is complaining that
miranium mining isn't meeting projections.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0012
rows.name: Well, that's a pickle.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0013
rows.name: Fine, we'll get out there and install some new probes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0014
rows.name: Otherwise, tell 'em to work with what they got. Get creative.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0015
rows.name: Mustache man seem very low-key...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0016
rows.name: Yeah... Is this supposed to make his job seem all stressful?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0017
rows.name:
Ah, there you are! I assume you witnessed that
elegant display of high-stakes multitasking?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0018
rows.name: Uh...not exactly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0019
rows.name:
Well, it's still early.
Come find me in the afternoon when things really heat up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0020
rows.name: Wait, what?! We have to do this AGAIN?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0021
rows.name: That's an order![ST:wait ]
